<h2><a class="listing" style="document" href="/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Developments/Innovation-and-Inclusive-Development" title="Innovation and Inclusive Development  " alt="document">Innovation and Inclusive Development  </a></h2>

	
	
	
	
					<p>By <b>Lynn Mytelka</b>, Professorial Fellow, UNU-MERIT, France &nbsp;&nbsp;While many small changes that collectively modify products and processes may open up opportunities for including smallholders in the innovation process, Lynn Mytelka anticipates that there are challenges in developing capabilities, strengthening linkages and building a support infrastructure at the local level.&nbsp;</p>
